text: Yekaterina Nikolayevna Mulyuk-Timofeyeva or Katsiaryna Mikalayeuna Muliuk is an archer from Belarus. Mulyuk-Timofeyeva competed at the 2008 and the 2012 Summer Olympics. She was born on 13 November 1976.Katsiaryna Muliuk-Timofeyeva == References == Category:Belarusian archers Category:Olympians for Belarus Category:1976 births Category:Living people
